{
  "text": "The frequency of OSAS is high in patients with acromegaly. Hern\u00e1ndez-Gordillo et al. performed polysomnography in 35 acromegaly patients and they found that 34 patients (97%) with AHI of \u22655 had OSAS [CITATION_1] patients (56%) were diagnosed with OSAS [CITATION_2] . In our study, we also showed that 25 out of 28 (89.3%) patients were diagnosed with OSAS, and we concluded that OSAS is very common in acromegaly.",
